{
  "stem": "1169.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And my mother said, you know, [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It cannot be.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Now, here is a man who comes from one of the concentration camps in Poland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He comes to a rabbi, and we did not believe him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "To this day, I feel bad for this man that he was very upset.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "That we doubted this.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But the Germans were such masters of deception, that we who were in it and see a man running away from it, we still would not believe it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I think that this is significant.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I really was not completely aware of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only knew there was a big war, and we are on the other side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I knew that [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] they-- over in a lot of Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I did not to look at the Germans, let's say, as the fathers of Nazis and war with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had them right home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "To us, the Nazis were the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in some respects, they were more Nazis than the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even their leader, [INAUDIBLE] Hitler, came from Austria.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I knew there was a struggle for our survival, for our existence.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I did not really realize the full detail.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's important to remember that we did not have television, we did not have radio, and the press was very limited.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We just knew what we heard.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] There wasn't an awareness, like today.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I know from history the exact scope of Nazism.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon the Jewish stores had to close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the Hungarian Nazis themselves became more verbal, more loud, more dominant, more eminent.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Every day, they had new regulations.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "New rules, new regulations.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
